name: Sara Simms & Melleefresh - Kreator (OBJKT One)
description: Sara Simms & Melleefresh team up on Kreator, a techno and drum’n’ bass tinged stormer. This three-part NFT collection features the work of Ukrainian makeup artist @tutushka_makeup. Melleefresh is an avant-garde performance artist who is originally known for her vocal work in Nelvana's Care Bears as Cheer Bear and Baby Tugs. Sara Simms is DJ/producer from Toronto into techno, music technology & turntablism. @sarasimms @melleefresh
